  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      AAE581 is a specific inhibitor of the cysteine protease cathepsin K. This trial is designed
      to provide detailed information about the effects( efficacy and safety) of AAE581 on Bone
      Mineral Density.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
